				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I have read posts where a lvl 60 Beast lord vs a Lvl 60 epic mage have dueled.
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Neither healed / buffed their pets or cast at all.  Purely a pet vs pet encounter.  From what they posted 9 out of 10 times the beastlord pet won.  Cant say as I can prove it as I have yet to try it.  But soon I will.  Still....if true I think it should put the question to rest.  If 9 out of 10 times a beastlord wins in a purely pet vs pet fight...then there should be no more arguing.  Still would be nice if some of you that have both classes at that lvl would try it out and see.
<br />

<br />

